Job Description
This position requires interaction with F&A;
/ FP&A; Leadership and Service Delivery teams, and Area/Sub Area in terms of process improvement (Six sigma ideas implementation)
Finance Teams to assess the effectiveness of existing processes and develop new or improved processes to meet changing business needs.
Analyze F&A; operations and processes and identify opportunities for improvements.
Participate in the implementation of process improvement initiatives.
Understand and support to the quality and metrics strategy team, including the ability to do effective process analysis, review quality results, customer reported issues, customer satisfaction results, perform root cause analysis, and identify opportunities for improvement.
